   {
      "body" : "I can personally promise you that I was not aware of the effect of making bare multisig nonstandard when this change was proposed. I believe this is a bug, and it should be fixed.\r\n\r\nI do, in addition, think that bare multisig is something that should be made non-standard over time, because there is no security benefit to storing full public keys in the UTXO set over simply a hash. That's a personal opinion, and open to discussion. It is not something that should happen as an unintentional side-effect of an unrelated change.",
      "created_at" : "2016-06-30T13:08:01Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/8079#issuecomment-229652491",
      "id" : 229652491,
